3VF_Y_PWC_PPL_AGEGRP_C.@EndUserText.label: 3VF_Y_PWC_PPL_AGEGRP_C
3VF_Y_PWC_PPL_AGEGRP_C.@DataWarehouse.sqlEditor.query:
SELECT DISTINCT "Gender" AS "GENDER_EXTERNAL_ID",
	"CSRD_Contract_Type" AS "CONTRACT_STATUS_ID",
	"CSRD_Working_Time" AS "WORKING_TIME_ID",
	"Location" AS "BUSINESS_LOC_EXTERNAL_ID",
	'Y' AS "PERIOD_TYPE",
	"YEAR" AS "PERIOD_YEAR",
	'CUSTOMER_PROVIDED' AS "SOURCE_EXTERNAL_ID",
	'PPL_HEADCOUNT' AS "MEASURE_ID",
	"Agegroup_ID" AS "AGE_GROUP_ID",
	SUM("EopHc") AS "MEASURE_VALUE"
FROM "3VF_HEADCOUNT_AGE_GROUP"
GROUP BY "Gender", "CSRD_Contract_Type", "CSRD_Working_Time", "YEAR", "Location", "Agegroup_ID"
